This is the layout for running GM and IM+IE in concurrent mode on 3 or 4 PE-s
or serial mode (but different root PE-s) on 2 PE-s.

Name First Last Stride
======================
#COMPONENTMAP
GM       0    2    1   ! GM runs on 2 PE-s
IM       2    2    1   ! IM runs on 1 PE
IE       3    3    1   ! IE runs on 2 PE-s
#END
